id: pm-c98b
title: Deduplicate lazy dynamic-import cache boilerplate in CLI registration
description: "Duplicate audit 2026-05-22: CLI registration modules repeatedly hand-roll nullable promise caches and import wrappers. Representative copies: src/cli/main.ts:227-242 loadSetupRegistrationModule, src/cli/register-mutation.ts:22, src/cli/register-list-query.ts:23, src/cli/register-operations.ts:21, and src/cli/register-setup.ts:15. Existing searches found closed main.ts decomposition and cache items, but no active item for the core CLI lazy-import helper pattern."
type: Chore
status: closed
priority: 3
tags[4]: cli,code-quality,dedup,startup
created_at: "2026-05-22T19:16:54.832Z"
updated_at: "2026-05-24T01:53:18.367Z"
author: codex-duplicate-audit
acceptance_criteria: A small shared lazy-module/once-import helper owns the nullable promise cache pattern; registration module import boundaries and startup behavior stay unchanged; focused CLI registration/startup tests and pnpm build pass.
parent: pm-rnpb
resolution: Closed by extracting the lazy module import cache helper.
expected_result: CLI registration modules share one lazy import helper while preserving startup/import behavior.
actual_result: createLazyModule was extracted to src/core/shared/lazy-module.ts and adopted across CLI registration files via PR #54.
